<h1>Password Reset Request</h1>

<p>Hi {{ firstName }},</p>

<p>We received a request to reset your password. Click the button below to reset it:</p>

<p>
  <a href="{{ resetLink }}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #007bff; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold;">
    Reset Password
  </a>
</p>

<p>Or copy and paste this link:</p>
<p><code style="background: #f4f4f4; padding: 8px; border-radius: 3px; display: inline-block;">{{ resetLink }}</code></p>

<p><em>This link expires in {{ expiresIn }} minutes.</em></p>

<hr/>

<p>If you didn't request a password reset, please ignore this email. Your password will remain unchanged.</p>

<p>Stay secure,<br/>The Security Team</p>
